verbose_text: The qPCR results showed that expression of miR-24-1-5p, miR-26a, miR-26b, miR-107 and miR-125b-5p were found to be increased in partially ligated LCA endothelium as compared to non manipulated RCA in APPsw-Tg mice and expression levels of these miRNAs were higher than those of non Tg mice LCA, whereas miR-125a-3p, miR-296-3p, miR-541-5p and miR-342-3p were decreased in APPsw-Tg mice compared with non Tg mice, but expression patterns of miR-242-5p and miR-26-3p were not different between APPsw-Tg mice and non Tg mice.
evidence: miR-125b-5p were found to be increased in partially-ligated LCA
